# -*- mode: org -*-

* Changelog

** (0.11.0) -- 2023.09.27

*** Added
- Add ~kosz-build-build-docs~ functions for build ~.texi~ files.

- Download package dependencies for test step.

*** Changed
- Add ~kosz-ui~ feature.

- Rename ~kosz-build-package~ to ~kosz-ui-build-package~.
  Move to ~kosz-ui~ feature.

- Rename ~kosz-build-and-install-package~ to
  ~kosz-ui-build-and-install-package~.
  Move to ~kosz-ui~ feature.

- Rename ~kosz-build-vc-package~ to ~kosz-ui-build-vc-package~.
  Move to ~kosz-ui~ feature.

- Rename ~kosz-build-and-install-vc-package~ to
  ~kosz-ui-build-and-install-vc-package~.
  Move to ~kosz-ui~ feature.

- Rename ~kosz-test-package~ to ~kosz-ui-test-package~.
  Move to ~kosz-ui~ feature.

- Rename ~kosz-build-build~ to ~kosz-build-build-package~.

- Rename ~kosz-utils-validation-error~ to
  ~kosz-manifest-manifest-validation-error~.

- ~:readme~, ~:src~, ~:src-exclude~, ~:docs~, ~:docs-exclude~, ~:assets~,
  ~:assets-exclude~, ~:tests~ and ~:test-exclude~ properties should not contains
  ~.~, ~..~, ~/~ or empty strings.

- Put builded packages in ~build/pkgname-pkversion/~ directory.

- Improve docstrings.

- Refactor code.

*** Fixed
- Fix error while processing ~:src-exclude~, ~:docs-exclude~, ~:assets-exclude~
  and ~:test-exclude~ properties.

- Fix unable to load feature in manifest file.

- Fix error when manifest without named properties is readed as nil.

** (0.10.1) -- 2023.09.13
